{"content": "<p>The 10k Residence is open to holders of the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\">10K Project</a>. </p><p>751 were airdropped their 10K Project on Sunday (those who filled out the Google Form) for being one of the first 10,000 frens to follow @mintfaced.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-10-at-10.06.11-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"938\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-10-at-10.06.11-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-10-at-10.06.11-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-10-at-10.06.11-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-10-at-10.06.11-PM.png 2110w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\">10K Project</a></figcaption></figure><p>Another couple of hundred have been <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523470586617675776?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1523470586617675776%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mintface.xyz%2Fclaim-your-10k-project-nft%2F\">given out on Twitter</a> for free + gas for finding your pfp in the artwork. If you haven't claimed yours, do it :)</p><p>Simply share the <em>row and column number</em> of your pfp with @mintfaced on Twitter and the wallet address for the private sale.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-2.43.59-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1850\" height=\"876\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-2.43.59-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-2.43.59-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-2.43.59-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-2.43.59-PM.png 1850w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>1x 10K Project = 1 unit in the 10K Residence</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"10k-residence-location\">10K Residence Location</h3><p>Your row and column co-ordinates also double as your floor and apartment number in the 10K Residence. Example:</p><p>Row 41 = Level 41<br />Column 66 = Unit 66<br /></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSiNaGfaQAAu0Qw.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1004\" height=\"984\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/FSiNaGfaQAAu0Qw.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/FSiNaGfaQAAu0Qw.jpeg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSiNaGfaQAAu0Qw.jpeg 1004w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Soooo...you already know your location in the 10K residence or if you need a hint, ask MintFace for a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced\">GIF CLUE</a>. </p><p>Visit some of the apartments being built as we speak.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSg2hCmacAAfMSU.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"876\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/FSg2hCmacAAfMSU.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSg2hCmacAAfMSU.jpeg 876w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/vlw_photography_loft_lyfe\">VLW Photography residence</a> 96th floor, unit 62</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FShNRM1UcAAE2Rj.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"868\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/FShNRM1UcAAE2Rj.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/FShNRM1UcAAE2Rj.jpeg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/FShNRM1UcAAE2Rj.jpeg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/FShNRM1UcAAE2Rj.jpeg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/wearyland?coords=-4.68x2.88x-6.96x-1.82\">Weary's Apartment</a> on the 91st floor, unit 49</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSjIpUQXEAAPf0I.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1574\" height=\"809\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/FSjIpUQXEAAPf0I.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/FSjIpUQXEAAPf0I.jpeg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSjIpUQXEAAPf0I.jpeg 1574w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://t.co/taslfxbVKp\">One Raw Artist</a> on 70th floor, unit 79</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.09.12-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"987\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.09.12-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.09.12-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.09.12-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.09.12-PM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/spaces/ISL3FC5Nbc6P9gwNKCkx\">Mike Shinoda's (Linkin Park) apartment</a> 61st floor, unit 49</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-5.01.52-PM-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1038\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-5.01.52-PM-1.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-5.01.52-PM-1.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-5.01.52-PM-1.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-5.01.52-PM-1.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/verymasa\">DigginNFTs pad</a> on Floor 27, unit 68</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.14.18-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1001\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.14.18-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.14.18-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.14.18-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.14.18-PM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><\na href=\"https://oncyber.io/ragmi?coords=3.64x2.90x-7.26x0.37\">Articulate's home</a> 10th floor, unit 53</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSi8evWXMAEMcgs.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1854\" height=\"805\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/FSi8evWXMAEMcgs.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/FSi8evWXMAEMcgs.jpeg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/FSi8evWXMAEMcgs.jpeg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/FSi8evWXMAEMcgs.jpeg 1854w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://twitter.com/E_0_I_N\">@E_0_I_N</a>'s pad on the 8th floor, knock on number 30</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.29.45-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1178\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.29.45-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.29.45-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.29.45-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.29.45-PM.png 2380w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>MintFace's apartment at an undisclosed location in 10K Residence</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"create-your-apartment\">Create Your Apartment</h3><p>Now for the fun part. <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/create?coords=0x2.30x0.00x0\">Kit out your apartment</a> with your favorite art thanks to OnCyber.</p><p>The rules:<br />1. Lofts or Pods only as this is the 10K Residence is...well its for residents :) We work and play elsewhere.<br />2. Put the 10K Project on display in your unit.<br />3. Share them with MintFace on Twitter!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Keep them coming! <a href=\"https://t.co/BitNBltNS0\">pic.twitter.com/BitNBltNS0</a></p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523960495916855298?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 10, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/create\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.11-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1698\" height=\"986\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.11-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.11-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.11-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.11-PM.png 1698w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/create\">Choose the Cyber Loft</a> for your 10K Residence</figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.22-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"697\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.22-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.22-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.22-PM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-12-at-3.16.22-PM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/create\">Choose a Pod</a> for your 10K Residence</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"who-is-welcome\">Who Is Welcome</h3><p>Everyone! Eventually. For now, in the first phase it is open to the first 10,000 people who followed MintFace on Twitter only. </p><p>Once everyone who wants to be in 10K Residence is setup and cosy...then we will look to open it up more widely.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">10K Project Residence is CDB friendly <a href=\"https://twitter.com/cathsimard_?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@cathsimard_</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/gJpDGqWz8A\">https://t.co/gJpDGqWz8A</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/SlUDUMnypM\">pic.twitter.com/SlUDUMnypM</a></p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1524551633472229376?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 12, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><h3 id=\"10k-residence-location-in-om\">10K Residence Location In Om</h3><p>We will select the perfect location for you to be able to walk to work, enjoy the bustle of the om city and see the beautiful art on display. The exact location will be released once the 10K Residence is fully constructed.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/location-and-size.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"995\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/location-and-size.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/location-and-size.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/location-and-size.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2022/05/location-and-size.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Location in om to be confirmed. It is not the building with the purple x on it</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"what-is-the-benefit\">What Is The Benefit</h3><p>You get to come home to a place where frens like us have been hanging out and enjoying each others company for the last year already...on Twitter. You will know many of your neighbours, and be able to wave to them in the lobby as frens come and go. </p><h3 id=\"what-does-it-cost\">What Does It Cost</h3><p>Right now...probably your eyesight to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523470586617675776?s=20&amp;t=vi8z95rmRIdrY4OrflZnqg\">find your pfp on the 10K Project</a> art! 😁(sorry we had to get really bot proof on this one). </p><p>Here is a <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/claim-your-10k-project-nft/\">high resolution 10K Project edition</a> to search through row by row.</p><p>If you buy an 10K Project you will also get access to the 10K Residence in Phase 2 but priority will go to the first 10K Residence.</p><p>The great frens at OnCyber are picking up the tab on the loft space, or you could pick up a Pod if you've got a little eth.</p><h3 id=\"what-to-do-next\">What To Do Next</h3><ol><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523470586617675776?s=20&amp;t=vi8z95rmRIdrY4OrflZnqg\">See if you are eligible</a> for a 10K Project free mint +gas.</li><li>If eligible, then <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\">share your row + column on Twitter</a> to get a 10K Project private sale invite.</li><li>If not, you can pick up a <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\">10K Project</a> if someone is selling.</li><li> <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/create\">Create your loft space</a> with OnCyber for the 10K Residence.</li><li>Share your OnCyber loft URL with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfacess\">@mintfacess</a> along with your row and column deta\nils.</li><li>We will then link your OnCyber loft into the 10k Residence.</li></ol><hr /><p>Cooool.</p>"}